### Health - Gateway
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Health - Account Service
GET http://localhost:8081/health

### Submit Credit Event
POST http://localhost:8080/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-Trace-ID: trace-demo-001

{
  "eventId": "evt-001",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "CREDIT",
  "amount": 150.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:02:11Z",
  "metadata": {
    "source": "mainframe-batch",
    "batchId": "B-9042"
  }
}

### Submit Debit Event
POST http://localhost:8080/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-Trace-ID: trace-demo-002

{
  "eventId": "evt-002",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "DEBIT",
  "amount": 40.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:05:11Z",
  "metadata": {
    "source": "mobile-app"
  }
}

### Duplicate Submission - Should Not Double Apply
POST http://localhost:8080/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-Trace-ID: trace-demo-001

{
  "eventId": "evt-001",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "CREDIT",
  "amount": 150.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:02:11Z",
  "metadata": {
    "source": "mainframe-batch",
    "batchId": "B-9042"
  }
}

### Read One Event
GET http://localhost:8080/events/evt-001
X-Trace-ID: trace-demo-read

### List Events For Account
GET http://localhost:8080/events?account=acct-123
X-Trace-ID: trace-demo-list

### Read Account Balance
GET http://localhost:8081/accounts/acct-123/balance
X-Trace-ID: trace-demo-balance

### Read Account Details
GET http://localhost:8081/accounts/acct-123
X-Trace-ID: trace-demo-account

### Gateway Custom Metric
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/event_gateway_events_accepted_total

### Account Service Custom Metric
GET http://localhost:8081/actuator/metrics/account_service_transactions_applied_total
